e the regular dynamic-access strategy, which iterates through uncovered classes and refines coverage class by class, this strategy gives the agent the full dynamic-access report in one prompt and asks it to cover the missing accesses in a single broad pass.\\\",\\nforge/strategies/predefined_strategies.json:535:      \\\"optimistic-dynamic-access-iteration\\\": \\\"prompt_templates/dynamic_access/optimistic-dynamic-access-iteration.md\\\"\\nforge/strategies/predefined_strategies.json:548:    \\\"description\\\": \\\"Pi graphify-assisted bulk dynamic-access strategy. It first builds graphify context from downloaded source artifacts, then gives the agent the full dynamic-access report in one broad pass. Unlike the regular dynamic-access strategy, it does not run the class-by-class refinement loop.\\\",\\nforge/strategies/predefined_strategies.json:553:      \\\"optimistic-dynamic-access-iteration\\\": \\\"prompt_templates/dynamic_access/optimistic-dynamic-access-iteration.md\\\"\\nforge/strategies/predefined_strategies.json:567:    \\\"description\\\": \\\"Codex graphify-assisted bulk dynamic-access strategy. It first builds graphify context from downloaded source artifacts, then gives the agent the full dynamic-access report in one broad pass. Unlike the regular dynamic-access strategy, it does not run the class-by-class refinement loop.\\\",\\nforge/strategies/predefined_strategies.json:572:      \\\"optimistic-dynamic-access-iteration\\\": \\\"prompt_templates/dynamic_access/optimistic-dynamic-access-iteration.md\\\"\\nforge/strategies/predefined_strategies.json:592:      \\\"optimistic-dynamic-access-iteration\\\": \\\"prompt_templates/dynamic_access/optimistic-dynamic-access-iteration.md\\\",\\nforge/strategies/predefined_strategies.json:593:      \\\"dynamic-access-iteration\\\": \\\"prompt_templates/dynamic_access/dynamic-access-iteration.md\\\"\\nforge/strategies/predefined_strategies.json:614:      \\\"optimistic-dynamic-access-iteration\\\": \\\"prompt_templ